  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">IEC61850-9-1 /2</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;" translate="true">IEC61850-9-1 / IEC61850-9-2 is different protocol type of IEC61850. user should set to correct mode according the actual IED device.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="clip0016.png" scale="70.00%" width="645" height="484" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">User can import from a defined SCD/CID/ICD file or load from a saved file to quickly start the configurations.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">The &quot;Scout&quot; button provide an online SV detection.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">IED selection:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="clip0017.png" scale="70.00%" width="640" height="154" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;" translate="true">This area allow to select connected IED device.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;" translate="true">Fiber channels mapping:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="clip0018.png" scale="70.00%" width="643" height="191" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt;"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">This area allow edit and mapping the SV channels to a logic channel which displayed on all the test modules.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal;" translate="true">&quot;Set as G1-6&quot; are the shortcut button map to Group1 - Group 6.</text></para>
